        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Support for Community Bridges Act</strong></p> <p>This bill sets aside a portion of Federal-aid highway funding for repairing structurally deficient bridges that are not part of the National Highway System and prescribes a formula to allocate this funding to states based on their share of such bridges.</p> </p>]]>
        </text>
